## Involvement Levels Guide

- **High**: Daily/weekly interaction, key decision maker, critical to success
- **Medium**: Regular check-ins, informed of major decisions, important but not critical
- **Low**: Occasional updates, peripheral to project, awareness-level only

---

## Template for New Stakeholders

When adding new stakeholders, include:
- Name, role, organization (required)
- Contact information (required)
- Involvement level (required)
- Key concerns (what matters to them)
- Communication style (how they prefer to work)
- Champion/Skeptic/Neutral (their stance)
- Decision authority (what they can approve)
